channel.title: New to everything
channel.description:
Alright, I've been playing rs roughly since late '01, and I've never really been aware of this side of the Rs community until now. I don't even know what half the stuff listed on the forums are, if even that.
So, could you guys be so kind as to introduce a new member into whole new world?
For example: Who/what is mopar? Whats aryan and scar? Rs has hacks? etc.
I know this might be in the wrong forum, but as it seems to get the most attention, maybe I'll get better answers to all my questions.
Thanks for reading,
-W
